Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.52,0:00:07.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Wednesday Downtown,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.04,0:00:09.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let’s get on with our first presenter please
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.43,0:00:19.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's Jinnai Tomonori!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.25,0:00:23.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Good relationship, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.34,0:00:24.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let's get to the point
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.94,0:00:25.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please take a look
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.50,0:00:35.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,2nd Among the people you know, if you confess in the order of how much you like them, and you'll find someone within 100 people, no matter who you are
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:37.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The ending of the 1st edition previewed the 2nd
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.41,0:00:38.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But what happened the first time around?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.88,0:00:40.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please see the review
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.40,0:00:44.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The last to test this hypothesis was...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.76,0:00:48.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Papa's Hoshino Disco
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.32,0:00:51.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who confessed to he liked in the order of how much he liked them
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:54.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At the 16th person...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:57.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please go out with me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.17,0:00:59.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh--?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:01.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,With Miyuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.77,0:01:08.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I have discussed the matter that I like Disco
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.23,0:01:10.79,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It came out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.65,0:01:14.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A succesfull coupling
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.72,0:01:16.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Or so it seemed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.16,0:01:19.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As expected... Ito...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.23,0:01:23.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I like you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.56,0:01:26.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But we haven't been out on a proper date yet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:30.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He was told "i'll consider it after a date"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.96,0:01:30.96,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.67,0:01:35.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As he couldn't give up on the 13th person, Ito Chinami
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.79,0:01:38.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He ultimately didn't choose Ami
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.39,0:01:40.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And after a few meetings with Ito
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.85,0:01:44.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He confessed again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.42,0:01:49.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you can, please go out with me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.39,0:01:50.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,However
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.46,0:01:55.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can't get into a relationship with you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.28,0:01:59.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, he failed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.82,0:02:05.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, Ami, who clearly confessed but was rejected
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.57,0:02:09.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Didn't Disco do this project?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.84,0:02:12.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.51,0:02:13.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can I try it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.28,0:02:17.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I want to have a boyfriend, really
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.72,0:02:19.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,With all my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.17,0:02:18.99,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Volunteered?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.31,0:02:22.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And so, the 2nd edition follows suit
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.13,0:02:27.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ponloop Ami's 100 person confession project!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.87,0:02:44.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, Kanda, this theory
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.71,0:02:46.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you did it, there'd probably be no problem
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:48.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think so
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.21,0:02:49.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's 100 people, after all
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.61,0:02:52.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't even know 100 people
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.62,0:02:53.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah right
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.12,0:02:54.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Shibuya?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.55,0:02:56.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, honestly... \N -Confident?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:59.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Confident
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.29,0:03:00.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.79,0:03:05.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If its 100 people, it should be possible
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:10.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,To validate this theory
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.53,0:03:13.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Now is not the time to be indecisive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:19.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,With 5 years of experience, Pon Loop's Ami, 28 years old
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.61,0:03:22.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,By the way, how has your love life been so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:24.27,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Couldn't have dressed up a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.81,0:03:27.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So far... the number of years without a boyfriend equals my age
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.55,0:03:32.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Neither confessed nor been confessed to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.72,0:03:37.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The majority of students at her high school were girls
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:40.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And in college she became passionate about comedy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:46.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's how Ami has never experienced love head-on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:52.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I kind of think it's time for a relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:53.98,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seems like a good girl
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.43,0:03:58.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, she was asked to seriously consider the person she wanted to date for a week
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:02.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The day of confession arrives
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:04.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Only the thought of a relationship is on my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.50,0:04:06.28,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Determined
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:09.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ami's first choice is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:09.46,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not bad, not bad
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.30,0:04:13.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oswald's Ito
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:16.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The first time we met was about 3 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.55,0:04:15.17,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.63,0:04:16.28,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Picked him as number one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.64,0:04:18.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It was love at first sight, so to speak
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:20.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.01,0:04:23.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Hello"\N  -You've worked hard
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.98,0:04:26.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Want to meet
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.31,0:04:27.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Hey, what? What's wrong?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.43,0:04:31.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Called Ito to TBS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:34.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Her first confession in life begins
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.08,0:04:34.22,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Looks kinda nervous
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:34.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:36.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.89,0:04:38.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:38.81,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The wind is so strong
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:40.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Could you please have a seat first?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.43,0:04:42.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:44.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,On the bench? \N -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.33,0:04:49.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although it may be insignificant to you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.17,0:04:51.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When recording a show with you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:54.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,With your group and mine
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.67,0:04:59.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In the backstage, the atmosphere was pretty cold
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.14,0:05:02.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At that time, only Ito came to our side
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:04.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.52,0:05:09.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Don't worry so much about whether this works or not. It's okay."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.33,0:05:08.87,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So gentle
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.09,0:05:10.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is what you said to me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:12.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You probably don't remember
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:15.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.69,0:05:18.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was really saved by those words
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:18.22,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The bangs
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:21.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Gradually, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.64,0:05:21.34,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A handsome vibe appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:30.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Think I like Ito
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:28.51,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The back is flowing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.90,0:05:31.11,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What kind of haircut is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.11,0:05:32.40,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Like a character actor
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:33.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:35.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I like you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.61,0:05:39.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I like Ito
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:43.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Would you go out with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:42.92,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Very clear and direct
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:46.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:05:52.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.30,0:05:55.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm very sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.53,0:06:00.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ami is unfortunately rejected by her first choice
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.14,0:06:05.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I just see you as a junior
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:08.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A close junior
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:11.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is that what you think of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:12.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's for sure
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:15.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well that also makes me happy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:17.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,To be honest I think it's quite suspicious
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.86,0:06:19.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The phrase "cute junior"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:23.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's fine to be a "cute junior"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.03,0:06:27.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And he said it casually
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:31.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As its just the first person, I'm starting to realize
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:32.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's starting to get a bit scary
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.00,0:06:36.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But i'll continue with a positive mind
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:37.96,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:37.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:41.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The second place is Shogo
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:41.80,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,They're all comedians
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.49,0:06:43.39,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:48.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, I think it's not possible
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:52.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It is better to have a good relationship but also distance with juniors
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:55.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah...  \N-That's what I think
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:59.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She's still a "cute junior"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:02.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.16,0:07:02.45,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Another comedian
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:09.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"I just see you as a junior"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.91,0:07:13.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"That's all I've thought up until now"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.31,0:07:19.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That is, as a fellow comedian
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.90,0:07:16.48,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Youtuber？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:22.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"I think of you as an interesting senior"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:21.59,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Comedy writer
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:25.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"I think of you from that perspective."\N  -Hmmmmmmmm
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.78,0:07:27.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.73,0:07:33.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"I have a girlfriend at the moment"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.06,0:07:35.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.17,0:07:35.13,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,College junior
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:38.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I thought none of them have girlfriends
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:42.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I took this into consideration when making the list
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.17,0:07:43.91,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.38,0:07:48.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,From her first confession in life, Ami is rejected by 6 people in 3 hours
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.89,0:07:52.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In 7th place is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.12,0:07:55.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Timon D's Maeda
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:56.68,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Unexpected choice
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:58.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We have a good relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.09,0:08:00.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And we go out to eat
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.86,0:08:02.08,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is a different thing from falling in love
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:03.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We also go to concerts together sometimes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.82,0:08:09.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The closest male so far, Maeda
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:11.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much. Sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.27,0:08:14.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you can
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.71,0:08:17.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Would you be able to go out with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:19.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ahhh so
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:22.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, that, yes...
