Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.19,0:25:45.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Good
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.09,0:25:45.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm tired already
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.65,0:25:50.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So Ami confessed to 71 men she likes
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.44,0:25:51.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But she wasn't successful
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.94,0:25:53.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But she was serious
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.25,0:25:54.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She really wanted to get a boyfriend on the same day
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.83,0:25:55.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But there was no way to do it that day
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.96,0:25:56.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's this?  \N-Impactful words
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.97,0:25:59.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Same-day boyfriend
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.13,0:26:01.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She wanted it on the same-day, but couldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.51,0:26:07.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, with Juicemans' Yojiro, and the promise of going on a date
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.25,0:26:11.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Things were getting heated
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.58,0:26:12.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ami did start to get angrier and angrier
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.40,0:26:16.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Gradually more and more angry
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.49,0:26:19.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It became a bit like trying to emotionally pressure people to borrow money
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.62,0:26:22.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are situations where she was surely angry
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.39,0:26:23.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, now, Ami
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.78,0:26:26.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is going on a date with Yojiro
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.40,0:26:28.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,By the time this episode airs
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.09,0:26:35.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It'll be clear whether they are in a relationship or not
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.10,0:26:39.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So the results will be stated in the broadcast
