Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.48,0:26:42.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yojiro is the 19th. \N -19th place
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.07,0:26:43.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not bad, not bad
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.98,0:26:47.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's okay.  \N-It's okay
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.42,0:26:52.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So a week after the confession
