Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.24,0:27:01.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.41,0:27:06.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After that, they met a few times
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.51,0:27:10.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What the hell is going on here?
