Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.79,0:27:19.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,One month from the start of the confessions
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.72,0:27:23.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Finally it's time to confess again
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.86,0:27:29.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We've had frequent contact, we've met frequently
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.03,0:27:35.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,More than before, I like you more now...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.87,0:27:41.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think I really like you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.31,0:27:45.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although its nothing new
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.54,0:27:53.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you can, can you go out with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.62,0:27:55.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.32,0:27:59.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, well, well, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.70,0:28:04.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ami who wants her first boyfriend
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.28,0:28:10.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And Yojiro who had a girlfriend once 6 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.75,0:28:15.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The answer given is...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.41,0:28:20.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At the beginning of the confession, the first time, to be honest it was a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.94,0:28:23.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I felt a lot of pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.85,0:28:25.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did I apply pressure?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.58,0:28:28.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, unsurmountable pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.39,0:28:32.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But in terms of dating, it felt good
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.09,0:28:33.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You seemed to be really happy
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.96,0:28:36.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And i've been very happy being with you
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.29,0:28:38.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I've felt really happy
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.60,0:28:41.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Its made me happy
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.43,0:28:42.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.37,0:28:49.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think, if we were to be together, I think we'd both be very happy
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.11,0:28:57.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, I'd also like to ask you to be with me \N -Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.21,0:28:58.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh eh eh eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.58,0:29:01.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh eh eh eh, what!?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.45,0:29:10.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Does that mean I've become Yojiro's girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.03,0:29:10.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah that's the case
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.66,0:29:35.32,note_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}※The BGM is Disco's song... yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.20,0:29:16.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.23,0:29:18.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please take care of me
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.03,0:29:20.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Too awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.14,0:29:26.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I hope you'll delete Disco-san's contact information immediately
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.64,0:29:28.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I will talk to Disco
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.48,0:29:29.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ami is mine
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.51,0:29:32.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We're doing a joint performance together, so we'll have to meet
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.48,0:29:34.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If I meet him, I'll definitely beat him up
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.35,0:29:35.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please don't
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.75,0:29:36.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.49,0:29:39.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.16,0:29:41.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I really though it was hopeless
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.99,0:29:43.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It really didn't seem like it was going to work out
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.29,0:29:45.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was rejected by 71 people!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.16,0:29:46.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I never thought this would be the result
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.03,0:29:49.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What kind of date do you want in the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.67,0:29:51.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hmm, how to put it
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.87,0:29:54.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Go once to... go to Disneyland once
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.70,0:29:57.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go book it now
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.20,0:30:05.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next is everybody's theories
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.05,0:30:07.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Tonight's presenter is
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.40,0:30:12.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's Tamura Kenji!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.90,0:30:14.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Tam Ken?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.19,0:30:17.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm Tam Ken, thank you for waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.37,0:30:20.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So guys, let me ask you a question about curry
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.80,0:30:24.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you hate curry, please raise your hand and explain why
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.42,0:30:26.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't think I hate it
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.63,0:30:28.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.08,0:30:34.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So this time, I bring you the second part of a certain curry theory
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.51,0:30:36.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is it
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.08,0:30:43.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The 2nd - If the smell of curry wafts in from the next room during a meeting, you'll surely go eat curry afterward
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.49,0:30:47.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah yeah this was done before
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.84,0:30:49.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.71,0:30:55.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The plan is to keep sending the aroma of curry to the next room during a meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.49,0:31:02.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And then fellow the target on the street to see if they eat curry or not
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.76,0:31:03.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.88,0:31:05.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This did happen
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.48,0:31:07.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Five out of six people ate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.65,0:31:09.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah\N -It was pretty impressive
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.96,0:31:13.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Only Noda Crystal did not eat
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.40,0:31:18.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because he hates curry
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.06,0:31:21.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped. \N -It can't be helped. After all, people who hate curry will definitely not eat it
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.61,0:31:27.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Basically, we can say that the theory has been proven, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.23,0:31:30.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But... those people last time
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.40,0:31:35.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They're all simple-minded guys, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.79,0:31:37.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It varies from person to person, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.23,0:31:42.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As soon as they smell the curry, they wanted to eat it
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.87,0:31:49.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, the next step is to re-examine curry in a new format
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.95,0:32:01.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The 2nd - If the smell of curry wafts in from the next room during a meeting, you'll surely go eat curry afterward
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.89,0:32:10.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time, we called our targets to the Green Mountain Studio under the pretext of a fake location for a TV show promotion
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.02,0:32:15.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In the middle of the discussion, they will smell curry coming from the next room
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.04,0:32:21.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then they'll choose their lunch from three possible menus
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.08,0:32:22.95,special_Wed_1_X,,0,0,0,,{\\fs55\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(307,922)}{\fad(100,0)}Ramen
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.08,0:32:22.95,special_Wed_1_X,,0,0,0,, {\\3c&H3025D2&} Curry
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.08,0:32:22.95,special_Wed_1_X,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1221,940)} {\3c} Omelet
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.59,0:32:29.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Incidentally, in front of the curry cart, we set up a trap
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.26,0:32:30.45,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What a mess \N -Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.10,0:32:34.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although perhaps a bit unreasonable for people attracted by the smell
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.73,0:32:36.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We'll let them fall regardless
