Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.44,0:32:49.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm Plus Minus' Iwahashi, thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.68,0:32:52.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Plus Minus' Iwahashi
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.23,0:32:53.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And
