Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.63,0:43:05.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Shoji Tomoharu
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.21,0:43:12.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Here he is also asked some questions about diet and lifestyle
