Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.24,0:43:48.90,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.06,0:43:52.20,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Completely and perfectly confirmed
